      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and feeling great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll feel the same way once you get behind the wheel! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you might have, so feel free to reach out!",
      "price": 28500.0,
