    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333 hp with exceptional linear response. Power is managed via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and both rod bearings and VANOS solenoid maintenance have been completed. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics, providing precise turn-in and high lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping and patina consistent with a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited B-road use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
